latestPosts.caption:
Morning Water (on waking)
Warm water with lemon + soaked nuts
.
🍳 Breakfast (8:00–9:00 AM)
Vegetable Moong Chilla (2 medium) with mint chutney
1 boiled egg or 2 egg whites (Optional for non-eggetarians)
1 cup masala chai with less sugar OR black coffee
Calories: ~350–400
.
🍛 Lunch (1:00–2:00 PM)
1 cup cooked  rice or 1 medium jowar roti
1 cup mixed veg sabzi (with minimal oil)
1 bowl dal
Cucumber + tomato salad with lemon and salt
Calories: ~400–450
.
🍲 Dinner (7:30–8:30 PM)
1 bowl quinoa pulao + beetroot curd
Calories: ~350–400
 .
Night Water (5:00–6:00 PM)

1 glass jeera or saunf (fennel) infused water
(Soaked for 30 mins in warm water)
.
🔚 Total Calories: ~1200–1300 kcal
.
Balanced macros: Complex carbs, moderate protein, low fat
.
Indian-friendly spices and ingredients
.
‼️ This is a sample diet plan. Diet Plans are far more effective when they’re customized.‼️
